column419:
BUas is considering the development of a 1 year, English taught professional Master called “AI-Translator”. The target group are domain-specialists: students with a bachelor’s degree in Tourism, Hotel management, Facility Management, Leisure and events management, Logistics, Built Environment, Creative Media & Games Technology or Creative Business (all non-AI bachelor programs within BUas). 

 The aim is to educate people that speak the language of AI-specialists, are able to initiate and manage data projects and are aware of the ethical and organizational consequences of such projects.
